      "side": 1,
      "message": "This isn\u0027t going to scale: what will happen when we will want to support other brokers? (e.g. AWS Kinesis, Kafka, ...)\n\nAdding all of them as dependencies would end up in a dependency hell and would force us to make unlikely compromises between releases.\n\nPlease see my comment in adding support to publish to the events-broker and have other plugins to provide the concrete implementations.",
